{"tid":202882,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺有抑鬱症焦慮症唔應該比佢地返工","createTime":"2017-04-15T22:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T01:33:33.000Z","uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42c38cc87331f089cafadb4aff981ce9931dd89b","tid":202882,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:42:40.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過啲同事同客人感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3261ea6d912933a04e7ca61101b25bedec6ac4c2","tid":202882,"uid":51134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:48:14.000Z","msg":"香港地10個有8個都帶病返工架啦<br />\n手停口停呀<br />\n有得抖邊個唔想"},{"pid":"830762b76941a94a36f0133b21cec86f2a3c50e2","tid":202882,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:50:22.000Z","msg":"你比錢我呀"},{"pid":"54e5f5b8b4550c1d67ebcc1ead5f465c9c768099","tid":202882,"uid":101558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T23:05:36.000Z","msg":"佢地都係人<br />\n點解唔可以返工?<br />\n唔係應該更加要欣賞佢地帶住咁多既負面都肯努力去服務社會既咩"},{"pid":"6c8d369364a7bf914df4ec420dd4207166ac2d76","tid":202882,"uid":48165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T23:10:03.000Z","msg":"一念無明成套戲就係屌緊樓主呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf741ae7820353205598b4963339e7eddccf442","tid":202882,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T23:12:41.000Z","msg":"最好就流落街頭，人道毀滅，視而不見？<br />\nLive with that啦，你/身邊人遲早都有咁既一日<br />\n學習下點相處好過"},{"pid":"3876b8dcacfd9307b2dddd60b21c3069201379ed","tid":202882,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:14:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港地10個有8個都帶病返工架啦<br />\n手停口停呀<br />\n有得抖邊個唔想</blockquote><br />\n而家係根本大家就哂佢做埋佢個份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de90fa294322855234079f735c62fea402173caf","tid":202882,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:13:09.000Z","msg":"問心個同事成日遊魂同做錯野喎，真心ok咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9063efb58f4d662d90a6f49435358e353ea71f0e","tid":202882,"uid":18302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T16:42:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問心個同事成日遊魂同做錯野喎，真心ok咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有精神病唔代表佢會遊魂同做錯野架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相反 有啲抑鬱病人係因為對自己要求太高 搞到壓力太大先會有事<br />\n好多時精神病都同工作能力無乜關係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解而家仲有人有啲咁嘅偏見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9e7799ac14905c416832ad82ebab754d3b1aa9","tid":202882,"uid":43398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T19:45:38.000Z","msg":"病人已經無力到連自己感受都顧唔到控制唔到，你仲叫佢顧埋其他人感受？<br />\n就係你呢類人搞到佢地就算懷疑自己出左事都唔敢正視 因為你呢啲仆街知道佢地有病之後只會冷言冷語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df9d6d89b28f2c24d9694a1f8093624e46e6b03","tid":202882,"uid":84331,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T20:56:43.000Z","msg":"仆街黎講樓主都算係表表者，祝樓主早日成為抑鬱病人之一"},{"pid":"e52c9e6939cc11f5a2502dd70ce77f22b65960a1","tid":202882,"uid":60435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:31:12.000Z","msg":"其實有好多人都係潛在患者<br />\n只要無同你講 你就唔會用個病黎標籤佢<br />\n如果我9up話一個無病嘅人係患者<br />\n你就會搵到好多野抽秤佢"},{"pid":"1c263fe6a0ebea8610482a8bb956e8c8ea812ca8","tid":202882,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:33:33.000Z","msg":"咁如果病到做唔到野就應該休息下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正式病假, 糧照出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}